data.description: This is the best-priced Gulf Access POOL home in Cape Coral with more than 2k sq. ft., built in 2002 with NO BOAT LOCK OR LIFT, and it's off Pelican! This home offers a NEW roof, NEWER pool heater, approx 2,200 sq ft of living space, 4 bed-2 bath-2 car garage, on a rarely available lot with approx.140 ft of waterfrontage and partial lake views! The oversized primary bedroom has access to the lanai area and room for a private sitting area.  With 2 large walk-in closets, dual vanities, a separate tub, and a shower, the master ensuite layout functions perfectly! The large open kitchen offers an island, pantry, and plenty of room for multiple chefs to work! Want to create your dream kitchen? You will love the amount of space you have to work with! The backyard offers an open lanai pool area, pool bath and plenty of room to build your dream custom dock! With some love and creativity, you can craft this blank canvas into the waterfront home you've always dreamed of!  Make your appointment to see it today! With it's generous waterfrontage, ample living space, and incredible potential, start living the dream or make it a successful vacation rental...your choice!
